snippet.title: Arcade Game: Great Swordsman (1984 Taito)
snippet.description:
A sports-based 1-on-1 sword-based fighting game that spans 3 types of sword fighting : Fencing, Kendo, and gladiator-style combat.

Note: Used Invincibility cheat when toward the end of the first round.
